; Coverage for xact.cc lines 1138-1144 (auto_xact state inheritance)
; Auto-generated postings inherit cleared/pending state from the
; parent transaction.

= Expenses
    (Budget)    -1

2024/01/01 * Cleared Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 ! Pending Test
    Expenses:Rent    $500.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Budget --format "%(cleared ? \"C\" : (pending ? \"P\" : \"U\")) %(payee) %(amount)\n"
C Cleared Test $-10.00
P Pending Test $-500.00
end test
